com.betfair.cougar.core.api.ev.processors

Class PostMatchingInterceptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betfair.cougar.core.api.ev.processors.PostMatchingInterceptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExecutionPostProcessor

    public class PostMatchingInterceptor
extends Object
implements ExecutionPostProcessor
    If the provided Matcher does in fact match the outbound invocation, the provided ExecutionPostProcessor is invoked, otherwise InterceptorState.CONTINUE is returned. If no Matcher is provided, ALL inbound requests will be deemed to match (which is ok as long as you intend to add a matcher later, otherwise there is no need to use this interceptor!)
